nodes.text: Zeenada was a marshy planet primarily covered in jungles.

Zeenada was invaded by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars. The Galactic Republic sent clone trooper forces to retake the planet, led by Anakin Skywalker and Ahsoka Tano. The planet was soon freed from Separatist control.
Zeenada was home to a variety of dangerous creatures, including a type of feline predator that inhabited its jungle, and a type of reptilian creature that made its home in the swamps.
